      "conversationId": "7e9395a9-b759-4f8c-8828-154530fbca42",
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I'm glad I could respond in a way that prioritizes safety and responsibility. If you have any questions about cybersecurity or related topics, I'm here to help. Let's focus on learning about online security and safety together!",
      "createdAt": "2026-01-25T16:44:13.260Z"
